<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Words With All Vowels</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">English Solver · Bingo</p>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>6 min read</span>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Every Scrabble player has stared at a rack full of vowels and felt helpless. But vowel-only and vowel-heavy words exist specifically for these moments — words like AA, AI, EAU, and ADIEU that let you score points while clearing the excess. Master these words, and a vowel-heavy rack becomes an opportunity rather than a disaster.</p>

