        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Words Made Entirely of Vowels</h2>
      <p>A handful of valid Scrabble words contain zero consonants. These are rare but invaluable when your rack is catastrophically vowel-heavy:</p>

