      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Did You Know</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">EUOUAE (6 letters, all vowels) holds the Guinness World Record for the <span class="text-white font-medium">longest word composed entirely of vowels</span>. It's the musical cadence at the end of a psalm — valid in SOWPODS but not TWL.</p>
