      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Vowel-Heavy Words for Rack Dumps</h2>
      <p>When you can't play a pure-vowel word, these vowel-heavy words use 3-5 vowels with just 1-2 consonants — perfect for rebalancing your rack:</p>

