          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">You can score 8+ points. You have ADIEU, AUDIO, or similar available. A premium square is reachable. Playing creates a hook for your next turn. Fewer than 7 tiles remain in the bag.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Exchange Instead</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Best available play scores under 5 points. No vowel-dump words fit the board. Exchanging 4-5 tiles gives you a fresh start. Many tiles remain in bag (early game). Opponent has a tight lead you need a bingo to overcome.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

