        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">⚠️ End-Game Rule</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">In the endgame (fewer than 7 tiles in the bag), <span class="text-white font-medium">never exchange</span>. You must play or pass. This is when memorised vowel-only words become absolutely critical — AA, AI, and OE can save you from being stuck.</p>
